  Kinetic (Delta T^0):                   1.000439588045772         27.2233           627.79          2626.65
  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.605202056136281        -16.4684          -379.77         -1588.96
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.197970586906877         -5.3871          -124.23          -519.77
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.040448833082938          1.1007            25.38           106.20
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.026187021345708         -0.7126           -16.43           -68.75
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.211528756739843          5.7560           132.74           555.37
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

